data.description: A must see 4 bedroom 2 bath home in the Crossings West at Bilbray Ranch. Fourth bedroom, without closet, can be used for an office or study. The home is 1600 sq ft with a two car garage. The backyard is fully fenced. Desert landscaping in the front yard. The backyard has artificial turf with mature landscaping. All landscaping is on automatic watering system. A covered patio with a stainless-steel barbecue grill that stays.  The home has tile in the kitchen and bathrooms. Bedrooms and living room are carpeted. The entry into the office has glass pane double doors. The living room has a slider to the covered patio.  The living room also has surround sound speakers in the ceiling. The primary bath has a tiled shower. The primary bedroom is roomy and has a view of the backyard. Jack and Jill bathroom between the two bedrooms with a tub shower. The kitchen has Corian countertops.  The kitchen eating area has a front window view. The garage floor is painted for easy clean up.
